PBS
```json
{
  "application": "PBS",
  "software": [
    "qsub",
    "qstat",
    "qdel",
    "blah_common_submit_functions.sh",
    "blah_job_registry_add",
    "blah_libexec_directory/pbs_local_submit_attributes.sh"
  ],
  "resource_requirements": {
    "memory": "pmem, pvmem, mem",
    "nodes": "select=1",
    "ncpus": "ppn",
    "mpi": "nodes, ppn, smpgranularity, hostnumber, wholenodes, mpinodes"
  },
  "environment_variables": {
    "pbs_spoolpath": "/var/lib/torque/spool",
    "pbs_binpath": "/usr/bin",
    "blah_libexec_directory": "/path/to/blah_libexec_directory",
    "blah_sbin_directory": "/path/to/blah_sbin_directory",
    "job_registry": "/path/to/job_registry"
  }
}
```
